<p>This is my first coded coffee/tea-shop website.<br>Do you <em>love</em> coffee just as much as I do? Well, if you do, this website is exactly right for you.<br></p>
<h2>This section is for all those four year olds that want to look as cool as their parents, making tea.</h2>
<p>
<li>First, plug in the ketttle</li>
<li>Pour a glass of water into a mug</li><li>Now open the lid of the kettle</li>
<li>Pour the water from your mug, into the kettle</li>
<li>Put the mug aside</li>
<li>After closing the lid of the kettle push down the red button on the kettle</li>
<li>Now, open your box of teabags, unwrap a teabag and put it into the mug</li>
<li>Now, after waiting for around three minutes for the tea to boil, all you have to do is open the tea kettle again and pour the, now hot tea, into your mug</li>
</p>
